title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Ray J Vs. Kardashians, Getting Toilet Paper In Your Mouth, Celtics And More!
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Talk Ray J Vs. Kardashians, Getting Toilet Paper In Your Mouth, Celtics And More!
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we talk about thee latest updates in Ray J Vs. Kim Kardashian in regards to the recent sex tape scandal... we chat about what he had to share on "Tha God's Honest Truth". Later we ask callers if they've ever gotten toilet paper stuck in their mouths after "eating"... For Donkey of The Day Charlamagne gives it to the Boston Celtics and you will see why...
